<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lei kisiem ma chun 'Thu' chuh a um,
 Pa Pathien tawh kumkhuo'n a kizawm;
 Bangkim abawnin Ama'n A siem,
 A siem loh a um puoi khawvel ah.

[V2]
 Zie thusim achun ka deihpen chuh,
 'Thu' chuh taksa a pieng in a um;
 A lop zie mupa'n a zik hi,
 'Lungsiet leh Thutak in a dim hi.

[V3]
 2. Thildang ahi puoi 'Thu' kiti hi,
 Krista Isu Amah ngei ahi;
 Mihing lungthim sung thu'n apawt hi,
 Pathien lungthim alang - Krista ah.

[V4]
 3. Pathien thiemgaute'n thu a gen ui,
 Angelte'n le a kihetsak sek;
 A sawl nunungpen pakchawih hitiu,
 Pathien-Mihing-A Chapa ngei chuh.</lyrics>
<title>THE WORD IS GOD</title>
</song>